object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM $$operational_schema.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = '$$sourcesystemcode'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT
    TRIM(metal_aeas.source_name) AS source_name,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.load_type) AS load_type,
    CAST(TRIM(metal_aeas.system_id) AS INT) AS system_id,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.parent_id) AS parent_id,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.cmm_container) AS cmm_container,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.id) AS id,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.assessment_id) AS assessment_id,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.solution_id) AS solution_id,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.solution_name) AS solution_name,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.business_function) AS business_function,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.assessed_entity) AS assessed_entity,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.category) AS category,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.score) AS score,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.score_percentile) AS score_percentile,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.normalized_score) AS normalized_score,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.recommended_action_description) AS recommended_action_description,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.recommended_action_code) AS recommended_action_code,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.conclusion_description) AS conclusion_description,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.conclusion_code) AS conclusion_code,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.score_date) AS score_date,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.assesment_detail) AS assesment_detail,
    TRIM(metal_aeas.error) AS error,
    CAST(TRIM(metal_aeas.row_id) AS BIGINT) AS row_id,
    cb.batch_id AS batch_id,
    bronze_aeas.acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_id,
    bronze_aeas.acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_md5checksum
FROM $$raw_schema.acx_ea_assessment_summary metal_aeas
LEFT JOIN $$staging_schema.acx_ea_assessment_summary bronze_aeas
    ON COALESCE(TRIM(metal_aeas.id), '') = COALESCE(CAST(bronze_aeas.id AS VARCHAR), '')
   AND CAST(TRIM(metal_aeas.system_id) AS INT) = CAST(bronze_aeas.system_id AS INT)
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(metal_aeas.parent_id), '') = COALESCE(bronze_aeas.parent_id, '')
   AND COALESCE(TRIM(metal_aeas.cmm_container), '') = COALESCE(bronze_aeas.cmm_container, '')
   AND bronze_aeas.acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
   AND bronze_aeas.acx_ea_assessment_summary_row_status = 'Active'
CROSS JOIN current_batch cb
ORDER BY 
    metal_aeas.system_id,
    metal_aeas.parent_id,
    metal_aeas.cmm_container,
    metal_aeas.id;
